description: Coming winter is making my hobby incredibly hard. It´s freezing all the time so streets are empty. It´s more difficult to find anyone cute who´s willing to talk, not to mention showing skin. After a long search, I met this adorable boy. He was waiting for his friend so he didn´t mind to talk in the meantime. He was a male nurse, which was really good because it´s one of the worst paid profession you can do. He was shy but my offers made him do crazy stuff. Despite the freezing cold and people driving by. He even agreed to take me to his friends apartment. I was so horny that I almost fucked him on the stairs in the hallway. He was too scared to do that but at least he sucked me off. The adrenaline rush was amazing! Then we moved to the flat and the real fun started.
title: Czech Hunter 330
